  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large frying pan over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute, until fragrant.",
    "Add the mixed bell peppers and cook for 3-4 minutes, until tender.",
    "Add the pepperoni and cook for 1-2 minutes, until crispy.",
